docs.summary:
The wix-blog-backend module contains functionality for working with
 your site's Wix blog.
Retrieves a category with the provided ID.
Retrieves a category with the provided slug.
Retrieves a post with the provided ID.
Retrieves a post with the provided slug.
Retrieves up to 100 categories, given the provided paging, filtering, and sorting.
description: To learn how to query categories, see [API Query Language](https://dev.wix.com/api/rest/getting-started/api-query-language).

docs.summary: Retrieves up to 100 posts, given the provided paging, filtering, and sorting.
description: To learn how to query posts, see [Field Support for Filtering and Sorting](https://dev.wix.com/api/rest/wix-blog/blog/filter-and-sort).

members.name: sort
members.doc:
Sort order by descending view count, ascending or descending publish date, or default to descending by publish date with pinned posts first.
One of:
 + `"FEED"`
 + `"PUBLISHED_DATE_ASC"`
 + `"PUBLISHED_DATE_DESC"`
 + `"VIEW_COUNT"`
